      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. I've babied this car since day one, and it's still looking and driving like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014not a scratch or a dent in sight. If you\u2019re looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
